allCategory.title: Fresh Coconut - 1 Piece
allCategory.body: This Fresh Coconut is a naturally cultivated food item with high mineral content. Its coconut oil helps to increase good (HDL) cholesterol and lowers bad (LDL) cholesterol. The coconut contains an abundance of fiber that keeps your digestive system healthy and helps to maintain regular bowel movement. This fresh coconut also provides water, milk, and coconut flesh that may aid in weight loss.

allCategory.body: Fresh and juicy premium chicken escalope that can be enjoyed fried, breaded or rolled. Delicious in every bite. For a hearty, yummy meal, add a tasty mushroom sauce and some mashed potatoes as a side. It's that simple!

Delicious caramelised and baked in the oven (use your preferred marinade for a juicy glaze) or breaded and fried. Serve with Gourmet Dip It Tzatziki and your preferred Gourmet fresh salad.
